snippet.title: Teaser - The Immemorial Order 2 - Sisters of Darkness
snippet.description:
Please enjoy the sort of teaser for the project I am currently working on. The game is in its very early stages. There is no release date yet but keep an eye out for more info soon.
Thank you for your continued support. It means the world to me :)

Check out my other games below.

The Immemorial Order
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2856310/The_Immemorial_Order/

The Immemorial Order VHS
https://wicksley.itch.io/vhs
